$interpreted: Pushing Commoner: A monster's coming! Run!!! Why's it so slow up there!!
Fleeing Commoner: Hey!! Quit pushing!!
Diana: Quit running around, it's dangerous! Please, everyone calm down! Please...
Ru-yi: Sophie! A monster is heading towards the Queen!!!
Sophie: Morgan's Marvelous Circus!!! Our assistance is required!
Sophie: Everybody is flustered and no one can hear what the Queen is saying...
Diana: The people never felt like I was there for them...
Diana: If I could just become a leader who the people could rely on, perhaps that would stabilize the situation...
Sophie: Your Majesty...
Sophie: Little girl, it's not safe here. Quick, get——
Sophie: Are you...the Holy Maiden Misa?
Misa: ...*sob*...*sob*...
Sophie: At least you're okay....wait a second, I got it!!!
Sophie: Holy Maiden, can you help us get everybody's attention?
Sophie: With your help, we can definitely calm the people down and get more of them out of here...
Sophie: Holy Maiden?
Misa: I-I-I'm no Holy Maiden!
Sophie: Huh? What do you mean?
Misa: I'm not the reincarnation of the Snake Goddess...I'm not...the High Priest said it was his medicine that gave me my powers...
Diana: Devious...I see. He used you...
Sophie: ...But nobody knows that! If you're willing to help, we can definitely do a lot more good and save more people!
Misa: No! I don't wanna!!!!!!
Sophie: Holy Maiden?
Misa: I don't wanna!!!! I'm nothing but a fake──
Diana: And what's wrong with being a fake? ──just become the real thing!
Diana: What makes you nothing, what takes away you're value...it's not Devious and it's certainly not me. It's nobody but...yourself.
Misa: ...**sniffle*...myself...?
Diana: ──Fulfill your duty. Don't let the people down, Holy Maiden Misa.
Sophie: Her Majesty is right, little Misa.
Misa: Little Misa...?
Sophie: Perhaps you're not a reincarnated goddess. But, right now, you can still save everybody.
Sophie: ...Only you can do it, little Misa.
Misa: I...can?
Sophie: Of course! Come on, get up!
Sophie: Ceres, we're back! How much longer can you hold on?
Charle: It's already too much for me to handle. I'll try my best to keep it up. Get as many people out of here NOW!!
Sophie: Where's the Queen?
Misa: She demanded that she stay behind. She'll be here soon...
Lazer: Diana!!!
Sophie: Wonderful, the Queen is safe.
Hutchinson: Headmaster, watch out!!
Charle: Oof!!
Diana: Ahh!!
Sophie: Your Majesty!!
Ru-yi: What should we do? The crack is sealing up! The Queen is still inside!
Hanbei: But if we go back in there, we'll be tr——
Lazer: !!!!!!
Sophie: That person...I knew it...it was all for the Queen...
Escaping Commoner: The one that just rushed inside...was that General Lazer?
Frightened Commoner: Are you kidding me!? What are we going to do? The High Priest became a madman out of nowhere!!
Frightened Commoner: Now the Queen and Lazer are both dead, there's no way we'll stay alive! We're screwed!
Sophie: Wait just a minute. There's still hope...
Frightened Commoner: This is the end of the Desert Kingdom!! Ahhhh!!!
Ru-yi: Is it...raining?
Hutchinson: I don't think so...but luckily everyone looks much calmer.
Frightened Commoner: It's the Holy Maiden! The Holy Maiden Misa!!
Escaping Commoner: She hasn't betrayed us!
Sophie: (You can do it, little Misa...!)
Misa: ...You...you still have me...
Misa: As-As long as I'm h-here, the Snake God will protect you...and won't allow the Desert Kingdom to fall to pieces!
Misa: I-I-I'm the Holy Maiden Misa...
Misa: Trust me, the Queen will restore peace!
Frightened Commoner: She's right! As long as the Queen and Misa are here, we'll never lose hope!
Escaping Commoner: Everybody, let's stay with the Holy Maiden! Long live the Queen!!! Long live the Holy Maiden!!!
